n over medium heat and add a little oil. Working in batches, place buns into pan, sealed side down, and fry for 3 minutes on each each side, until both sides are golden brown and crispy (see Tips). Serve while warm."}],"hintsAndTricks":["These buns will flatten and spread slightly as they cook in the frying pan.","You can replace the beef with pork in the filling."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","50m","10 pieces"]}